NK016(ma)018:1: // snga 'gyur bka' ma'i drag dmar 'o bran lugs kyi brgyud 'debs ni /
NK016(ma)018:2: khyab bdag gdod ma'i mgon po 'od mi 'gyur //
NK016(ma)018:3: 'phags mchog snying rje'i dbang phyug mig mi 'dzum //
NK016(ma)018:4: rtsa gsum kun 'dus pad+ma 'byung gnas la //
NK016(ma)018:5: gsol ba 'debs so mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)018:6: 'phags bzhi bskyed yum dbyings phyug mkhar chen gza' //
NK016(ma)018:7: grub pa'i dbang phyug 'o bran dpal 'byung dang //
NK016(ma)018:8: 'byung bzhir dbang bsgyur 'o bran dbang phyug la //
NK016(ma)018:9: gsol ba 'debs thog med mthu mnga' 'o bran chos 'byung dang //
NK016(ma)018:10: drag rtsal nus thob 'o bran grags pa'i mtshan //
NK016(ma)018:11: 'khor 'das dbang bsgrur 'o bran dbang rgyal la //
NK016(ma)018:12: gsol ba 'debs gsang chen mdzod brnyes 'o bran rta mchog rgyal //
NK016(ma)018:13: lta dgongs gdengs ldan 'o bran ri rab brtan //
NK016(ma)018:14: nyi ma rgyal mtshan kun dga' blo gros la //
NK016(ma)018:15: gsol ba 'debs rin chen chos rgyal tshul khrims dbang phyug dang //
NK016(ma)018:16: dkon mchog 'bangs dang dbang phyug rdo rje'i mtshan //
NK016(ma)018:17: gtsug lag rgya mtsho karma lung rig la //
NK016(ma)018:18: gsol ba 'debs so mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)018:19: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i nyi ma gter bdag gling //
NK016(ma)018:20: theg mchog bstan 'dzin kun bzang rnam par rgyal //
NK016(ma)018:21: gsang sngags bstan 'dzin mthu stobs rnam rgyal la //
NK016(ma)018:22: gsol ba 'debs so mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)018:23: mdzod lnga'i shing rta blo gros pha mtha' yas //
NK016(ma)018:24: thub bstan nyin byed rgyal mtshan 'od zer zhabs //
NK016(ma)018:25: bka' drin mnyam med rtsa ba'i bla ma la //
NK016(ma)018:26: gsol ba 'debs so mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)018:27: rab 'byams dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i spyi dpal che //
NK016(ma)018:28: che ba'i che mchog pad+ma drag po rtsal //
NK016(ma)018:29: gnas gsum mkha' 'gro rgyud gsum srung ma la //
NK016(ma)018:30: gsol ba 'debs so mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)018:31: dbang gi rgyud smin dam tshig rnam par dag /
NK016(ma)018:32: bskyed rdzogs don la rang byan tshud pa dang //
NK016(ma)018:33: mchog thun dngos grub yid bzhin grub nas kyang //
NK016(ma)018:34: mkha' mnyam 'gro ba kun bzang sar 'god shog //
